10) Troubleshooting & Runbook (step-by-step)
1. Confirm Node version: node --version -> must be >= 24.0.0
2. Install deps cleanly: rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json && npm ci
3. Run tests: npm test ; for coverage: npm run test:unit
4. If vitest errors: run npx vitest --run tests/unit/*.test.js --reporter verbose to see stack traces
5. If CLI syntax errors occur: run node --check src/lib/main.js to get parse errors, or run node src/lib/main.js --range 15 to exercise runtime path.
6. If distributed files cause unexpected repo state: re-initialize from agentic-lib source with npx @xn-intenton-z2a/agentic-lib init --purge (WARNING: overwrites distributed files)

